					<div class="comment-body">
						
							<p>I favour the 50/50 strong bread flour/00, left to prove the day before in the fridge to slow fermentation. Nice body and crust. Sometimes add a little chopped oregano to the dough.<br>Have time for the Margherita is the best topping, but also have a penchant for artichoke hearts and prosciutto, not to heavy on the topping.<br>Yum, is it wrong to have pizza for breckie?</p>
						
