                        </div>
                    
					<div class="comment-body">
						
							<p>For me a pizza should be piled high with good things so it explodes over the plate as you eat it. Home-grown tomatoes, onions, home-grown peppers, mozzarella cheese, fresh home-grown chilli, olives, mushrooms, it all goes on.</p><p>It might also be heresy but I've had some success putting chorizo and lemon zest on pizzas.</p>
						
					</div>
				</li>
				
