                        </div>
                    
					<div class="comment-body">
						
							<p>Nice review.  I've tried endless variations, but now like to use about 20% semolina in the dough to give a slightly rougher texture to the finished product. </p><p>I use a gas 3-burner barbie and pizza stone to bake the pizza, with the middle burner turned off (otherwise the pizza burns).  With the gas turned up full, this cooks in about 5-7 minutes.  The main problem I have is getting the pizza on and off the paddle!</p>
						
