<img class="author-profile-picture" src="http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/discussion/avatars/2011/02/05/Applespider/501c406d-1413-4a93-9224-be27347d906b/60x60.png" height="60" width="60" alt="" />
<a href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/discussion/user/Applespider" title="User profile page">Applespider</a>

                            
