							<p>I will definitely be giving this base a go and always dust mine with semolina, it seems to help it crisp and not stick to the tray.  I vary between making an authentic looking pizza and - more of a winter standby - using the pizza to shovel large quantities of melted cheese into my mouth. But never pineapple!  I stuck my nose up at cheese and pineapple ever since I was old enough to be trusted with cocktail sticks.  <br>My husband and do have a shared dream of going to New York and trying one of those huge, stringy cheese pizzas you see, an ambition we both realised was sparked by watching Teenage Mutant Hero Turtles in the 80's.</p>
						
