<img class="author-profile-picture" src="http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/discussion/avatars/2010/08/23/YummieMummie/98ebdad5-cd33-4ee6-9f59-d9a134012195/60x60.png" height="60" width="60" alt="" />
<a href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/discussion/user/YummieMummie" title="User profile page">YummieMummie</a>

                            
